 '''股份'''是[[finance|投資市場]]的一个单位用作 [[互助基金]]， [[有限合伙伙伴]]和 [[不动产投资信任]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.investopedia.com/terms/s/shares.asp|title=Shares Definition|publisher=[[Investopedia]]|last1=Chen|first1=James|date=February 23, 2018|accessdate=9 July 2013}}</ref> The owner of shares in the company is a [[shareholder]] (or stockholder) of the corporation.<ref>{{cite book|last=Hoang|first=Paul|title=Business and Management|publisher=IBID Press|location=Victoria|year=2007|pages=[https://archive.org/details/businessmanageme0000hoan/page/71 71]|chapter=1.4 Stakeholders|isbn=1-876659-63-7|url=https://archive.org/details/businessmanageme0000hoan/page/71}}</ref>  A share is an indivisible unit of capital, expressing the ownership relationship between the company and the shareholder.
